    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"layout":"doc.js","slug":"docs/api/uart","title":"UART"},"html":"<h1 id=\"uart\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#uart\" aria-label=\"uart permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UART</h1>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">uart</code> module supports communication with computers or devices using serial ports (UART). Use <code class=\"language-text\">require('uart')</code> to access this module.</p>\n<h2 id=\"class-uart\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#class-uart\" aria-label=\"class uart permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Class: UART</h2>\n<p>An instances of <code class=\"language-text\">UART</code> represents a UART port.</p>\n<h3 id=\"uartparity_none\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#uartparity_none\" aria-label=\"uartparity_none permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UART.PARITY_NONE</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">0</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Do not use a parity bit.</p>\n<h3 id=\"uartparity_odd\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#uartparity_odd\" aria-label=\"uartparity_odd permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UART.PARITY_ODD</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Use odd parity bit</p>\n<h3 id=\"uartparity_even\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#uartparity_even\" aria-label=\"uartparity_even permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UART.PARITY_EVEN</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">2</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Use even parity bit</p>\n<h3 id=\"uartflow_none\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#uartflow_none\" aria-label=\"uartflow_none permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UART.FLOW_NONE</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">0</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Do not use flow control.</p>\n<h3 id=\"uartflow_rts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#uartflow_rts\" aria-label=\"uartflow_rts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UART.FLOW_RTS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Use RTS flow control.</p>\n<h3 id=\"uartflow_cts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#uartflow_cts\" aria-label=\"uartflow_cts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UART.FLOW_CTS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">2</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Use CTS flow control.</p>\n<h3 id=\"uartflow_rts_cts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#uartflow_rts_cts\" aria-label=\"uartflow_rts_cts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UART.FLOW_RTS_CTS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">3</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Use both RTS and CTS flow control.</p>\n<h3 id=\"new-uartport-options\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#new-uartport-options\" aria-label=\"new uartport options permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>new UART(port[, options])</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">port</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> UART port number. This value should be less than max port number.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">options</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;object></code> The object of UART options. <em>Default values are depends on board (Check in a board page).</em>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">baudrate</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Baud rate. One of the <code class=\"language-text\">[0, 50, 75, 110, 134, 150, 200, 300, 600, 1200, 1800, 2400, 4800, 9600, 19200, 38400, 57600, 115200, 230400]</code>.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">bits</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Number of bits per a character. One of the <code class=\"language-text\">[8, 9]</code>. <strong>Default:</strong><code class=\"language-text\">8</code></li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">parity</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code>. The parity is one of the <code class=\"language-text\">UART.PARITY_NONE (0)</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">UART.PARITY_ODD (1)</code>, or <code class=\"language-text\">UART.PARITY_EVEN (2)</code>. <strong>Default:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">UART.PARITY_NONE</code>.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">stop</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Number of stop bits. One of the <code class=\"language-text\">[1, 2]</code>. <strong>Default:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">flow</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Flow control. One of the <code class=\"language-text\">UART.FLOW_NONE (0)</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">UART.FLOW_RTS (1)</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">UART.FLOW_CTS (2)</code>, or <code class=\"language-text\">UART.FLOW_RTS_CTS (3)</code>. <strong>Default:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">UART.FLOW_NONE</code></li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">bufferSize</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> The size of internal read buffer.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">tx</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> UART TX pin number. <code class=\"language-text\">-1</code> Not to use this pin. <strong>Default:</strong> board dependent. Check the <code class=\"language-text\">Boards</code> document.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">rx</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> UART RX pin number. <code class=\"language-text\">-1</code> Not to use this pin. <strong>Default:</strong> board dependent. Check the <code class=\"language-text\">Boards</code> document.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">cts</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> UART CTS pin number. <code class=\"language-text\">-1</code> Not to use this pin. <strong>Default:</strong><code class=\"language-text\">-1</code></li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">rts</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> UART RTS pin number. <code class=\"language-text\">-1</code> Not to use this pin. <strong>Default:</strong><code class=\"language-text\">-1</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Create the UART instance and close it</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">UART</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'uart'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">baudrate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">9600</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">bits</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">partity</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">UART</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">PARTIY_NONE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">stop</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">flow</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">UART</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">FLOW_NONE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">bufferSize</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2048</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> serial0 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">UART</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// read or write data...</span>\nserial0<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"writedata-options\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#writedata-options\" aria-label=\"writedata options permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>write(data[, options])</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">data</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Uint8Array|string></code> Data to write.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">options</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;object></code> \n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">count</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Indicates how many times to write data. <strong>Default:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Writes data to the UART port.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">UART</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'uart'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> serial0 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">UART</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">baudrate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">38400</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Write a string</span>\nserial0<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">write</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello, world\\n'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Write Uint8Array</span>\nserial0<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">write</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Uint8Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0x00</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x7f</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x80</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xff</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nserial0<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"close\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#close\" aria-label=\"close permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>close()</h3>\n<p>Close the UART port.</p>\n<h3 id=\"event-data\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#event-data\" aria-label=\"event data permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Event: 'data'</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">data</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Uint8Array></code> Received data.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">data</code> event is emitted whenever data is arrived (buffer size may varies).</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">UART</span> <span class=\"token 